  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  All patients with a large incisional hernia &gt;5cm diameter that needs elective repair
             with mesh augmentation

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  no written informed consent

          -  'hostile' abdomen

          -  emergency surgery (incarcerated hernia)

          -  parastomal hernia

          -  incisional hernia outside the midline

          -  recurrent incisional hernia
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
